description:
The Phoenix has had 2 huge defeats. Has this taken a toll on her? Does she still have the fire and desire to win? Will she still fight every second to take back control and turn the tables on a match or will she just coast though a match thinking it's all over for her? Smokie Flame? or Smokie Lame?
The Badger moved up a weight class and is wrestling better then ever before. Alexa Von Tess is kicking ass and taking names, and will not the the punching bag of Ultimate anymore.
title: Alexa Von Tess "The Badger" (3-4) Ranked 10th
